name: Calendar.Component
desc: An enumeration for the various components of a calendar date.

items.name: case yearForWeekOfYear
items.desc: Identifier for the week-counting year unit.

items.name: case quarter
items.desc: Identifier for the quarter of the calendar.

items.name: case weekOfYear
items.desc: Identifier for the week of the year unit.

items.name: case weekOfMonth
items.desc: Identifier for the week of the month calendar unit.

items.name: case weekdayOrdinal
items.desc: Identifier for the weekday ordinal unit.

items.name: case timeZone
items.desc: Identifier for the time zone unit.

items.name: static func != (Calendar.Component, Calendar.Component) -> Bool
items.desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether two values are not equal.
